caller_intent: The caller asked why they were charged $3,700 on their policy, believing they were on auto draft and expecting smaller payments.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the payment discrepancy and requested clarification on the policy type.
Agent attempted to check the policy details but admitted lack of access to the carrier's system.
Agent offered to transfer the caller to another agent for further assistance.
knowledge_required: Recognizing when to escalate to specialized agents
summary: Caller disputed a $3,700 policy charge, believing they were on auto draft. Agent could not access carrier details and transferred the call for resolution.
